data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Being sold as a short sale this 4 bed, 2 bath beauty is truly a spacious sanctuary that is ready to become your personal oasis. Step inside and be captivated by the open floorplan, designed with your comfort in mind. As you enter the living room, imagine cozying up next to the charming fireplace on chilly nights. Ceiling fans throughout the home provide a refreshing breeze on warmer days. The wood laminated floors create a seamless flow from room to room, adding a touch of sophistication to the space. Prepare to fall in love with the kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's paradise. Besides ample cabinetry and counter space, it features a delightful coffee station to start your mornings on the right note. The pantries offer plenty of storage for all your cooking essentials, keeping your kitchen organized and clutter-free. Escape to the primary bedroom, your private retreat. The double vanity, stand-up shower, and garden tub offer a luxurious spa-like experience. And let's not forget the walk-in closet, ensuring all your fashion treasures have their own special place.  The laundry room offers convenience and efficiency, making household chores a breeze. The other bedrooms are equally inviting, with sliding door closets and a shared bathroom featuring a shower/tub combination.  Step outside onto the deck and be enchanted by the backyard oasis. Lush trees provide shade and privacy, perfect for outdoor entertaining or relaxing with a book on a sunny day. Your own slice of tranquility awaits! Imagine the possibilities for your new home! Entertain loved ones in the spacious living areas, relax on the deck surrounded by nature, or indulge in the serenity of the master suite. This home truly has it all. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home. Call now to schedule a showing and experience the magic yourself. Your next chapter begins here!
